{"tid":1542002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布林鄭係全香港最識打文宣戰嘅人","createTime":"2019-09-04T17:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T17:37:50.000Z","uid":205919,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8a9a160bfa824a42a16891a9bd5e87f617960cf0","tid":1542002,"uid":205919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:20:51.000Z","msg":"見到連登熱門好多post講寶琳、太子、圍警署乜乜。<br />\n我明白個啲都係好重要。<br />\n但係！！<br />\n大家搞咁多野係為左乜？關注咁多野係為左乜？<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係想香港人嘅五大訴求可以達到！！！！</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而家仲有幾日，等美國過左個人權自由法案就贏架啦！</span><br />\n就差臨門一腳，比林鄭殺出一條咁嘅片！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其實真係好多外國人、台灣人以為我地贏左。</span></strong><br />\n而佢地咁以為得即係有機會美國議員都咁以為，到時條法案唔過，大家就係日日上網睇住香港唔同地區有手足出事架啦！！<br />\n所以我求你地危機意識高啲啦，我地輸緊啦<br />\n版上咁少post討論對外文宣同埋星期日集會！<br />\n幫手推對外文宣同星期日嘅野上熱門呀！！！<br />\n仲要翻譯做英文<br />\n我真係唔想大家辛苦左三個月就比林鄭一條片搞掂呀！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。"},{"pid":"052cdd61c60b08f4a314190c1f5e88e0590ad168","tid":1542002,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:21:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e87c8584a74a72b7d018abe6245809f507b78b8","tid":1542002,"uid":205919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20886b6adb4fb9f78379277f5ad229571528935a","tid":1542002,"uid":300514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:23:29.000Z","msg":"快啲加入twitter啦!!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n[圖文教學]覺得自己英文唔好但想加入twitter文宣戰線<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1541983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1541983</a>"},{"pid":"a5b7aadc002273fcf72b59560a6aad018c05fb80","tid":1542002,"uid":205919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:26:18.000Z","msg":"對外文宣呀！！！！<br />\n我要法案通過！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24b2ad8983cf0ddb6afa26f4d804a5d2a9bdc5c","tid":1542002,"uid":205919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:27:48.000Z","msg":"唔推我個post唔緊要<br />\n幫手推Twitter, 推9月8集會！！！！<br />\n同你啲外國朋友講香港未贏架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76ee350e8a86d238cec1cfd935738b43847e6fab","tid":1542002,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T17:28:06.000Z","msg":"撤回唔係為咗俾香港人降溫；<br />\n撤回係要分化外國政客、媒體，<br />\n令佢地失去插手香港局面既意慾。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人<br />\n約定你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/izm7G7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fizm7G7f.jpg&h=6080f594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aTJem7g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaTJem7g.jpg&h=c2ef69f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n九月八日 星期日</span></span><br />\